    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>New Yorker day is my favorite day of the week, too! I am right at this moment waiting for your apple bundt cake (aka bread in front of my health-conscious teenage son) to finish baking.</p>
<p>Sorry to hear everyone&#39;s sick. I just finished a great novel, The Snow Child by Eowyn Ivey, which really took me away to the wilds of Alaska, back in the days when a moose was enough &#8212; and often the only culinary option &#8212; to sustain a small family for the entire winter.</p>
    </div>

