    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>When I&#39;m sick I like to read engaging but untaxing chick lit. I recommend books by Jill Mansell and Katie Fforde. Both are British authors, books are set in England and have interesting characters you&#39;d like to live next door to. Feel better soon; there rule is the mothers are not allowed to get sick, or at least not allowed to give in to sickness.</p>
